1
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:15,439
You had clearly lost your mind,

2
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:16,920
how could you interrupt the ritual?

3
00:01:17,079 --> 00:01:18,680
This is impossible.

4
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:29,359
Sometimes,

5
00:01:32,040 --> 00:01:35,200
pain can keep a person awake.

6
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:38,760
Normally,

7
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:42,000
I'm actually terrified of pain.

8
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,040
Regardless,

9
00:01:44,159 --> 00:01:45,200
the Main Gate has opened.

10
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,280
What you've done

11
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:48,439
only delays the Celestial Realm's return.

12
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:50,400
When the Celestial Realm returns,

13
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,280
you

14
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,879
will still die.

15
00:01:54,599 --> 00:01:55,599
The Celestials' arrival?

16
00:01:56,079 --> 00:01:58,079
I'm quite looking forward to it too.

17
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,199
From now on,

18
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:15,080
the sea is boundless for fish to leap,

19
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,199
and the sky is high for...

20
00:02:17,159 --> 00:02:17,719
you.

21
00:02:35,439 --> 00:02:36,840
He just opened an immortal gate.

22
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,400
I wonder if inside him,

23
00:02:38,719 --> 00:02:40,159
a Celestial Seed will form.

24
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:42,360
I'm just going out for some air

25
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,960
and to get familiar with the area.

26
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,599
Do you believe me?

27
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:46,599
I do.

28
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:47,759
I know you don't believe me.

29
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:48,719
Have you had dinner?

30
00:02:48,879 --> 00:02:49,479
No.

31
00:02:50,719 --> 00:02:51,360
Perfect.

32
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:52,879
You need an empty stomach before surgery.

33
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:55,680
Surgery?

34
00:03:05,919 --> 00:03:06,520
Lie flat.

35
00:03:06,639 --> 00:03:07,560
Step one, sterilize.

36
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:09,439
Step two,

37
00:03:09,759 --> 00:03:10,439
get straight to it.

38
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,439
Am I going to die?

39
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:13,879
I'm a doctor,

40
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:14,960
not a killer.

41
00:03:18,759 --> 00:03:20,080
The anesthetic has expired.

42
00:03:22,599 --> 00:03:23,199
Sorry.

43
00:03:23,439 --> 00:03:24,199
Just bear with it.

44
00:03:28,639 --> 00:03:29,560
Got anything bigger?

45
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,319
Let me do it.

46
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,280
No Celestial Seed.

47
00:03:56,199 --> 00:03:57,479
Why is your face so pale?

48
00:03:58,319 --> 00:03:59,199
I forgot to stitch you up.

49
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,520
All done.

50
00:04:11,719 --> 00:04:13,680
It might be a bit ugly,

51
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,080
but it's very sturdy.

52
00:04:38,879 --> 00:04:40,120
Sleeping outside again?

53
00:04:40,279 --> 00:04:41,600
I told you you'd catch a cold.

54
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:02,319
Why'd he use so much thread on the stitches?

55
00:05:04,319 --> 00:05:06,399
Signs of infection are already showing.

56
00:05:06,839 --> 00:05:07,800
Honestly,

57
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,759
how does he forget to sterilize every time?

58
00:05:28,759 --> 00:05:29,519
The fever's gone.

59
00:05:44,399 --> 00:05:46,040
Another beautiful day.

60
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:48,680
And I'm still alive.

61
00:05:49,079 --> 00:05:49,759
Wonderful.

62
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,199
What is that?

63
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:11,439
Look, look!

64
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,480
Quick, look! A celestial!

65
00:06:13,639 --> 00:06:14,439
Come, come.

66
00:06:22,759 --> 00:06:23,439
Am I seeing this right?

67
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:27,480
Today I become an immortal!

68
00:06:27,639 --> 00:06:29,560
Chenxiang opens the mountain!

69
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:35,959
From this day on,

70
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:37,720
no one can bully me.

71
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,079
No one at all.

72
00:06:48,279 --> 00:06:48,879
I am

73
00:06:49,279 --> 00:06:51,199
The Blessed One of Chenxiang.

74
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:53,959
Quick, look!

75
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,319
What does "Blessed One" mean?

76
00:06:58,639 --> 00:06:59,560
How to cultivate immortality?

77
00:07:00,199 --> 00:07:02,439
Huge reward for any info on the Blessed One.

78
00:07:38,279 --> 00:07:41,079
We should be able to find the Celestial Seed now.

79
00:07:53,879 --> 00:07:54,560
Am I...

80
00:07:55,759 --> 00:07:57,199
Am I still alive?

81
00:08:05,759 --> 00:08:06,519
No.

82
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,639
This place is hell.

83
00:08:13,439 --> 00:08:14,160
I have to...

84
00:08:15,639 --> 00:08:16,319
I have to...

85
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:20,319
escape this madman's clutches.

86
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:18,360
Don't be afraid.

87
00:09:18,879 --> 00:09:19,639
Very soon.

88
00:09:48,679 --> 00:09:50,159
Welcome back, Immortal One.

89
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:52,799
Welcome back, Immortal One.

90
00:09:56,759 --> 00:09:58,720
Why hasn't the Celestial Realm returned?

91
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,840
What could have gone wrong?

92
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,639
May I ask, Heavenly Immortal,

93
00:10:08,159 --> 00:10:09,440
why is this happening?

94
00:10:10,639 --> 00:10:14,039
The Main Gate... it hasn't opened.

95
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:15,919
Su Yang, push the gate.

96
00:10:18,159 --> 00:10:19,559
Let us out!

97
00:10:19,639 --> 00:10:21,120
Let us out!

98
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:23,159
Let us out!

99
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,519
Here we go again.

100
00:10:25,639 --> 00:10:27,440
Let us out!

101
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,279
Whatever you want,

102
00:10:28,279 --> 00:10:30,440
we can handle it once we awaken.

103
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:34,320
Let us out!

104
00:10:34,639 --> 00:10:35,879
Let us out!

105
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:39,360
We can save your Tongtong, and also...

106
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:39,919
Shut up.

107
00:10:45,519 --> 00:10:46,720
The harder you kick,

108
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:48,480
the more you'll hurt yourself.

109
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:50,240
We share a symbiotic bond.

110
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:52,360
Stop this foolish behavior!

111
00:10:52,519 --> 00:10:53,519
Symbiotic?

112
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:56,559
So that means,

113
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:58,480
if I die,

114
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,840
you'll die too.

115
00:11:01,519 --> 00:11:03,080
Well, you should've said so sooner!

116
00:11:04,039 --> 00:11:06,919
Are you insane? You'll die like this!

117
00:11:07,519 --> 00:11:08,679
Do you really think

118
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:10,960
I'm afraid of dying?

119
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,200
May I ask the Holy Immortal's name?

120
00:11:27,799 --> 00:11:28,720
This Immortal

121
00:11:29,679 --> 00:11:30,600
is Zi Shu.

122
00:11:31,919 --> 00:11:33,440
Of the twelve zodiac signs,

123
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:35,200
Zi Shu.

124
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:38,000
Welcome to the mortal realm, Immortal One.

125
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:40,600
Welcome to the mortal realm, Immortal One.

126
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:43,320
What's your name?

127
00:11:44,279 --> 00:11:46,679
This humble Immortal Emissary is Wang Qiusheng.

128
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,320
Immortal Emissary?

129
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:54,000
Immortal Servant would be more fitting.

130
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:57,120
What is your current strength?

131
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:58,600
As long as we don't cross the authorities,

132
00:11:59,279 --> 00:12:00,559
within this city of Shanhai,

133
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:02,519
there's little we can't accomplish.

134
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,480
We were able to recruit members before

135
00:12:04,799 --> 00:12:05,879
because ancient texts recorded

136
00:12:06,519 --> 00:12:08,919
that the Immortal One could grant those without celestial fate

137
00:12:09,279 --> 00:12:11,000
a chance to step onto the immortal path.

138
00:12:11,879 --> 00:12:14,639
That's why they were so willing.

139
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:17,240
We hope the Immortal One

140
00:12:17,639 --> 00:12:19,360
could display a divine miracle.

141
00:12:20,279 --> 00:12:22,679
Please grant us your blessing.

142
00:12:23,679 --> 00:12:24,840
Work hard,

143
00:12:25,559 --> 00:12:26,919
and you'll naturally enter the immortal gate.

144
00:12:27,519 --> 00:12:28,879
From this moment on,

145
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,399
hunt down one person with everything you've got.

146
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,120
Shanhai City...

147
00:12:35,039 --> 00:12:36,039
Su Yang.

148
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:41,240
Stop! Stop!

149
00:12:41,759 --> 00:12:42,879
As long as you stop,

150
00:12:43,039 --> 00:12:45,679
whatever you want, we can negotiate.

151
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:47,679
That's right.

152
00:12:47,919 --> 00:12:49,960
We promise we won't start any more trouble.

153
00:14:39,639 --> 00:14:40,600
Stop! Stop!

154
00:14:40,919 --> 00:14:42,080
As long as you stop,

155
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:44,480
whatever you want, we can negotiate.

156
00:14:44,639 --> 00:14:45,200
That's right.

157
00:14:45,279 --> 00:14:47,480
We promise we won't start any trouble.

158
00:14:47,559 --> 00:14:48,559
I want all of you,

159
00:14:49,799 --> 00:14:51,279
from this day forward,

160
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:53,679
to obey me.

161
00:14:54,039 --> 00:14:54,919
Got it?

162
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:58,039
Yes, we agree.

163
00:14:58,039 --> 00:15:00,960
We'll all obey you.

164
00:15:01,519 --> 00:15:02,279
Very good.

165
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:06,600
I really look forward to our next meeting.

166
00:15:18,639 --> 00:15:19,440
Perhaps

167
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:22,240
to become a gang boss,

168
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:25,120
I'll always lack a bit of courage.

169
00:15:35,759 --> 00:15:36,559
Just now,

170
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:39,519
why didn't you kill me?

171
00:15:41,039 --> 00:15:41,720
I didn't dare.

172
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:44,039
If you killed me,

173
00:15:44,759 --> 00:15:46,440
I'd actually thank you.

174
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:47,840
Even if I killed you,

175
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:49,759
I still couldn't leave Black Street.

176
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:56,200
In your eyes,

177
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:59,360
what color is the sky?

178
00:16:01,639 --> 00:16:02,399
Blue.

179
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:05,000
And the clouds?

180
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:07,200
White.

181
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:09,399
But in my eyes,

182
00:16:10,559 --> 00:16:11,440
all of it...

183
00:16:11,799 --> 00:16:12,799
is black.

184
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:15,039
Pitch black.

185
00:16:23,159 --> 00:16:23,879
You're hungry.

186
00:16:25,759 --> 00:16:27,480
Right, you must be hungry.

187
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:30,519
There are a few cups of instant noodles in the kitchen,

188
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:32,960
on the cabinet.

189
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:35,360
If they haven't expired.

190
00:16:37,879 --> 00:16:39,679
You know, pain is a funny thing.

191
00:16:41,360 --> 00:16:43,159
Sometimes it stimulates your mind.

192
00:16:44,279 --> 00:16:45,840
But once you overcome it,

193
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:47,879
you stop being afraid.

194
00:16:49,039 --> 00:16:49,840
Instead,

195
00:16:50,679 --> 00:16:51,960
you start to enjoy it a little.

196
00:16:54,799 --> 00:16:56,200
What a madman.

197
00:17:08,519 --> 00:17:09,599
It seems they're

198
00:17:10,400 --> 00:17:11,799
getting a bit impatient.
